122
00:15:55,600 --> 00:16:05,760
Any aspirations or questions or intentions
that you may have.

123
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:19,820
Bring the hands together in pranam mudra,
in front of the heart, move into a round

124
00:16:19,820 --> 00:16:20,440
