168
00:22:41,700 --> 00:22:48,040
Maps help us find treasure in the same way
they've helped sailors find treasure.

169
00:22:53,920 --> 00:23:02,640
So I'm going to present some ideas around
koshas that hopefully are new to you.

170
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:30,120
As long as yogic ideas remain theory they
will not be relevant to our personal

171
00:23:30,120 --> 00:23:30,600
