179
00:24:34,700 --> 00:24:36,600
Okay, great.

180
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:39,400
So a very yoga aware group here.

181
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:51,440
So one of the first ideas of kosha is even
though it's five yogic bodies,

182
00:24:56,380 --> 00:25:04,060
it represents a continuum from gross to
subtle.

183
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:16,080
And before we even get into the five yogic
bodies, there are three bodies that come

184
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:17,260
before it.

185
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:33,250
They're often called gross, subtle,
and causal.

186
00:25:45,270 --> 00:25:48,610
And I won't go deep into the details of
the five yogic bodies.

187
00:25:54,150 --> 00:25:56,630
I won't go deep into this.

188
00:25:56,990 --> 00:26:00,990
But our gross body is the tangible body.

189
00:26:01,270 --> 00:26:05,790
The subtle body can be thought of like a
dream body.

190
00:26:06,090 --> 00:26:09,990
Sometimes in a dream you can feel yourself
moving around.

191
00:26:15,970 --> 00:26:19,250
Some traditions call it the astral body.

192
00:26:22,890 --> 00:26:28,550
And even the mental body, I can imagine
being in my home in Nepal moving around.

193
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:39,970
It's not philosophical.

194
00:26:40,490 --> 00:26:41,890
Humans have this.

195
00:26:42,030 --> 00:26:44,090
That's what makes all of this possible.

196
00:26:48,370 --> 00:26:52,370
We have the ability to move in imagined
spaces.

197
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:58,310
What's moving around?

198
00:27:01,030 --> 00:27:03,150
Think of that as the subtle body.

199
00:27:06,750 --> 00:27:10,150
Then there's the causal body.

200
00:27:10,490 --> 00:27:11,910
I don't know what that is.

201
00:27:15,290 --> 00:27:24,410
I understand it as an idea that from this
you get this, and from this you get this.

202
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,710
I'm trying to explain that.

203
00:27:38,890 --> 00:27:46,710
And in the longer retreat where we have
many more days, I will get into some ways

204
00:27:46,710 --> 00:27:49,730
of reflecting on the causal body.

205
00:27:53,170 --> 00:27:55,630
Then we can give them the information.

206
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:07,730
For those of you who have never heard of
the koshas or the five bodies,

207
00:28:07,930 --> 00:28:10,510
we're just going to quickly go over them
now.

208
00:28:17,170 --> 00:28:22,670
And keep in mind that they are just a
subdivision of these three.

209
00:28:29,710 --> 00:28:32,970
So we have the physical body.

210
00:28:35,330 --> 00:28:39,830
And whenever I say one of them,
please take your awareness into it.

211
00:28:40,210 --> 00:28:41,690
Don't let it be a word.

212
00:28:41,810 --> 00:28:42,970
Let it be an experience.

213
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:52,950
We have the energetic body.

214
00:28:56,890 --> 00:28:58,130
The mental.

215
00:29:02,430 --> 00:29:07,190
The intuitive, or for the moment I'm going
to use the word psychic.

216
00:29:12,330 --> 00:29:17,970
And then again, we reuse the word causal,
also referred to as blissful.

217
00:29:17,970 --> 00:29:24,630
Y vamos a usar de nuevo la palabra causal
o de bienaventuranza.

218
00:29:34,450 --> 00:29:40,970
Voy a decir las palabras en sánscrito
porque indican de qué están hechos estos

219
00:29:40,970 --> 00:29:41,450
